ore in The Mad Ones |first=Hannah |last=Vine |date=November 20, 2017 |website=Playbill }}</ref>}}\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''This Ain't No Disco''\n| Meesh\n| [[Atlantic Theater Company]]\n| {{small|[[Darko Tresnjak]]}}\n| {{center|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theatermania.com/off-broadway/news/this-aint-no-disco-casting_85171.html |title=Chilina Kennedy, Will Connolly, Krystina Alabado Set for This Ain't No Disco |first=David |last=Gordon |date=May 11, 2018 |website=Theater Mania}}</ref>}}\n|-\n| 2019\u2013present\n |''' ''[[Mean Girls (musical)|Mean Girls]]'' '''\n| '''Gretchen Wieners''' {{small|(replacement)}}\n| '''[[August Wilson Theatre]]'''\n| {{small|[[Casey Nicholaw]]}}\n| {{center|<ref name=\"playbill-mg-replacement\"/>}}\n|}\n\u2022 {{small| Credits in bold indicate Broadway production(s)}}\n\n== Filmography ==\n=== Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Year\n!Title\n!Role\n!Notes\n!Ref.\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[First Reformed]]''\n|Choir Member\n|\n|{{center|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BkGpkADD_e5/|title=Krystina Alabado on Instagram: \"Seeing myself on the big screen for the first time \ud83d\udc4d\ud83c\udffd I may not say much in this film, but I rock some SICK mens cargo pants #PaulSchrader\u2026\"|website=Instagram|language=en|access-date=2019-05-21}}</ref>}}\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Year\n!Title\n!Role\n!Notes\n!Ref.\n|-\n|2015\n|''[[Tyrant (TV series)|Tyrant]]''\n|Jill\n|Episode: \"A Viper in the Palace\"\n|\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[Voltron: Legendary Defender]]''\n|Veronica (voice)\n|Seasons 7-8 (13 episodes)\n|{{center|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BmTbmSDjauS/|title=Krystina Alabado on Instagram: \"The wait is over!! Friends, you can finally meet Veronica on the new season of #Voltron Legendary Defender on #Netflix streaming now!! She\u2026\"|website=Instagram|language=en|access-date=2019-05-21}}</ref>}}\n|-\n|2019\n|''[[God Friended Me]]''\n|Olivia\n|Episode: \"Miracle on 123rd Street\"